                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَوَصَّيْنَا﴾ أَمَرْنَاهُ، وَأَلْزَمْنَاهُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿كُرْهًا﴾ عَلَى مَشَقَّةٍ، وَتَعَبٍ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَفِصَالُهُ﴾ فِطَامُهُ.</h2>\n<p>﴿بَلَغَ أَشُدَّهُ﴾ نِهَايَةَ قُوَّتِهِ البَدَنِيَّةِ وَالعَقْلِيَّةِ.</p>\n<h2>﴿أَوْزِعْنِي﴾ أَلْهِمْنِي.</h2>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "46:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>...</p>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "46:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أُفٍّ لَكُمَا﴾ قُبْحًا لَكُمَا.</h2>\n<h2>﴿أَنْ أُخْرَجَ﴾ أُبْعَثَ مِنْ قَبْرِي حَيًّا.</h2>\n<h2>﴿خَلَتِ الْقُرُونُ﴾ مَضَتِ الأُمَمُ السَّابِقَةُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿يَسْتَغِيثَانِ اللَّهَ﴾ يَسْأَلاَنِ اللهَ هِدَايَتَهُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَيْلَكَ﴾ هَلَكْتَ.</h2>\n<p>﴿أَسَاطِيرُ الأَوَّلِينَ﴾ مَا سَطَّرَهُ الأَوَّلُونَ مِنَ الأَكَاذِيبِ فِي كُتُبِهِمْ.</p>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "46:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿حَقَّ عَلَيْهِمُ الْقَوْلُ﴾ وَجَبَ عَلَيْهِمُ العَذَابُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿فِي أُمَمٍ﴾ فِي جُمْلَةِ أُمَمٍ كَافِرَةٍ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿خَلَتْ﴾ مَضَتْ.</h2>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "46:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَلِكُلٍّ دَرَجَاتٌ﴾ وَلِكُلِّ فَرِيقٍ مِنَ الأَعْدَاءِ وَالأَشْقِيَاءِ مَنَازِلُ فِي القِيَامَةِ بِأَعْمَالِهِمْ.</p>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "46:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿عَذَابَ الْهُونِ﴾ عَذَابَ الخِزْيِ وَالهَوَانِ.</h2>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "46:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أَخَا عَادٍ﴾ هُوَ: هُودٌ عليه السلام.</h2>\n<p>﴿بِالأَحْقَافِ﴾ اسْمُ مَوْقِعِهِمْ؛ وَهُوَ فِي جَنُوبِ جَزِيرَةِ العَرَبِ.</p>\n<h2>﴿خَلَتِ النُّذُرُ﴾ مَضَتِ الرُّسُلُ.</h2>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "46:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿لِتَأْفِكَنَا﴾ لِتَصْرِفَنَا.</h2>"
        },
